-- Gazprom Considers Selling Almost Half of Novatek Stake, Interfax Reports
-- B y   A n n a   S h i r y a e v s k a y a
-- 2010-11-15T12:41:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/gazprom-may-sell-9-4-of-novatek-almost-half-of-stake-ifx-says.html
OAO Gazprom is considering the sale
of 9.4 percent of OAO Novatek, Interfax said, citing a bond
prospectus issued by the Russian gas export monopoly.  Gazprom, which holds 19.4 percent of Novatek, the country’s
second-largest gas producer, hasn’t made a decision about the
final terms of a sale, the news service said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anna Shiryaevskaya in Moscow at 
